Run the following in your browser's javascript console, and copy the output to a text file. Remove the quotes at the beginning and end of that output. Paste that text into a javascript console to restore the saved view.
"view = JSON.parse('".concat(JSON.stringify(CATMAID.WebGLApplication.prototype.instances[1].space.view.getView())).concat("'); CATMAID.WebGLApplication.prototype.instances[1].space.view.setView(view.target, view.position, view.up, view.zoom, view.orthographic); CATMAID.WebGLApplication.prototype.instances[1].options.camera_view = view.orthographic ? 'orthographic ' : 'perspective'; CATMAID.WebGLApplication.prototype.instances[1].space.render();")
